  "description": "<i>Raid on Gravitron</i> is a 1st person space shooter for the 8-bit Atari.<br><br>Played from 1st person perspective, the player tries to destroy a number of alien ships before their fuel runs out. The player fires a red laser, while alien vessels return fire which must be dodged.  Only one enemy ship appears on the screen at a time, and when they are destroyed, a new enemy appears.  The player has a limited energy supply, and the goal is to destroy all alien vessels before fuel runs out.    There is a training and combat mode of gameplay.  The player starts with 10 ships.  ",
